# In-Game Browser Testing

Before testing `index.html`, `src/main.js`, UI controls, project spawning, or in-game abilities in a browser, read `docs/IN_GAME_TESTING.md`.

Use that guide for Cursor Browser and Playwright runs. It documents the desktop controls panel, the mobile swipe-up bottom sheet, stale refs, coordinate-click rules, and the project-card flow needed to fire abilities such as `Stab!`.
